{
  "stem": "8834.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they took them out and-- and to shoot them too!",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was no good to do that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But they paid money for them to do that, or not to work so hard, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they beat them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this was awful-- awful what I saw-- what's-- what's going on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And where-- where the-- the girls, were once-- once I remember came a-- a commission-- a commission or a-- a delegation.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We did not know for what it is.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the-- the meister said there will be a delegation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You should-- you should come out in your best.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Look good.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And-- and dress as-- as much as you have to-- to come out and look good.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So we did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we stayed in line.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the-- and the commission looked at us-- how we look.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he says, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Come on out!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Sisters [NON-ENGLISH], come out!",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he said to the commission, look how they look.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we were young and had our clothes still from home-- looked not bad-- had-- had our-- had our health.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this was-- we were an example how the camp is running and how the camp's inmates look.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it wasn't so bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The commission saw the example.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then after that, we-- we realized what the-- who the commission was and why they took us as an example.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the Red Cross didn't have anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was a commission from the Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the commission didn't say anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it's not bad in there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They save my hair.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My sister had long, blonde hair.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They saved hers too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she washed it in black coffee.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had black, plain coffee.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So there was no hot water.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She washed it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they saved her hair.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
